content: But as you correctly point out, Manan, look, at the end of the day, as we get closer towards year-end, you're also going to see some impact on the expense side because many of our non-U.S. dollar assets can also be the expense part of those assets that we manage sometimes are in different areas around the world, which could have different currency impacts, and that could have an impact margin, specifically in the asset management business.
